    <h3>1) Hario V60 Dripper 02 White — Best Overall</h3>
    <p>The V60 02 remains the safest all-around recommendation because it balances availability, recipe flexibility, and long-term upgrade potential. If you eventually add a better grinder, temperature control kettle, or faster filter papers, this brewer scales with you instead of forcing a replacement. It also has one of the deepest recipe ecosystems online, which helps beginners troubleshoot quickly.</p>
