    <p>The Chemex 6-cup is a strong fit if your goal is one larger, cleaner pot with minimal bitterness and a presentation that looks as good as it brews. In practical terms, this brewer suits households that make multiple mugs at once and value clarity over body. The tradeoff is that it can feel less agile for quick single cups, especially if your grind dial-in is still evolving.</p>
