    <p>For buyers who want a full brewer-plus-carafe setup without spending much, this Melitta bundle is practical and straightforward. It trades some high-end flexibility for convenience and low barrier to entry. If your priority is "better than auto-drip flavor with minimal fuss," this is one of the easiest places to start before deciding whether to invest in a more technique-heavy workflow later.</p>
