    <h3>4) Hario V60 Switch Ceramic Immersion Dripper — Best Upgrade Pick</h3>
    <p>The V60 Switch hybrid format is ideal for brewers who like V60 flavor but want more control over drawdown timing. By using immersion before release, it can smooth out common beginner errors and increase consistency when your pour control is still developing. It is also useful when switching between brighter light roasts and more soluble medium roasts because you can adapt brew style without changing your entire setup.</p>
